<div id="specialbox2">
<h3>Where can I park?</h3>
<a class="showlink" href="#" id="faq10-show" onclick="showHide('faq10');return false;">Answer</a>
<div class="more_container" id="faq10"><br />
<div class="more_content">To avoid being ticketed, try to park in the temporary parking spaces in front of the Student Health Center reserved for SHC patients. If you are unable to park in one of these spots, temporary passes are available at our repception desk.</div>
